WEBVTT

00:00.100 --> 00:01.800
PREVIOUSLY
ON GHOST WHISPERER...

00:01.800 --> 00:04.700
THEY'RE WHAT'S LEFT OVER
OF OLD ROADS, ALLEYWAYS,

00:04.700 --> 00:07.700
THEY'RE WHAT'S LEFT OVER
OF ANOTHER TOWN-UNDERGROUND.

00:07.700 --> 00:09.400
Dad! YOU'RE ALIVE.

00:09.400 --> 00:11.000
IT HAS TO DO
WITH PAUL EASTMAN.

00:11.000 --> 00:13.200
YOU SENT HIM TO PRISON,
ONLY HE ESCAPED.

00:13.200 --> 00:15.100
I'VE PUT A LOT
OF PEOPLE IN JAIL,

00:15.100 --> 00:17.200
AND NONE OF THEM
HAVE COME AFTER ME.

00:17.200 --> 00:19.900
WHAT IF HE'S HIDING
FROM SOMEONE, SOMEONE WHO
HE SENT TO PRISON?

00:19.900 --> 00:21.600
WHAT IF HE'S JUST
LYING TO PROTECT ME?

00:21.600 --> 00:23.200
Jim: THE MAN KILLED
A LITTLE BOY.

00:23.200 --> 00:25.100
HE ESCAPED DURING
A PRISON FIRE.

00:25.600 --> 00:28.900
FACIAL BURN VICTIMS WEAR A
CLEAR MASK DURING TREATMENT.

00:28.900 --> 00:31.400
PAUL EASTMAN IS DEAD.
HE POSSESSED MY DAD.

00:31.400 --> 00:33.100
HE'S JUST TRYING
TO GET HIS REVENGE.

00:33.100 --> 00:34.400
I HAVE TO WARN MY DAD.

00:35.700 --> 00:36.500
DAD?!

00:38.100 --> 00:39.200
OH, MY GOD!

00:41.200 --> 00:42.200
Jim: TOM GORDON!

00:43.400 --> 00:44.400
TOM, WE'RE COMING IN.

00:47.300 --> 00:49.300
IT'S A GUNSHOT VICTIM.

00:49.300 --> 00:50.600
Man: WHAT ARE HIS VITALS?

00:50.600 --> 00:52.800
TOM, CAN YOU
HEAR ME, TOM?
LACERATIONS TO THE HEAD.

00:54.500 --> 00:56.700
HE MAY BE GOING INTO
FULL ARREST.

01:00.300 --> 01:04.599
I HAD TO. I HAD TO PROTECT HER, I HAD TO.

01:05.099 --> 01:06.800
TRY TO BE QUIET.
IT'S ALL RIGHT.

01:06.800 --> 01:08.000
I HAD TO.

