01:27.500 --> 01:30.100
YOUR FATHER'S IN
CRITICAL CONDITION, AND THE NEXT
24 HOURS ARE KEY.

01:30.100 --> 01:31.800
HOW COULD HE BE ALIVE?

01:31.800 --> 01:33.900
I SAW HIM,
I SAW HIS HEAD.

01:33.900 --> 01:34.900
COLD FEET.

01:35.600 --> 01:38.800
HE HAD THE GUN
RIGHT AGAINST HIS TEMPLE, BUT HE MOVED HIS HAND
JUST AS HE FIRED.

01:38.800 --> 01:41.000
MAYBE HE CHANGED HIS MIND
AT THE LAST SECOND.

01:41.600 --> 01:44.700
NOW THE BULLET HAD LODGED
UNDER THE SCALP, BUT IT DIDN'T
PENETRATE THE SKULL.

01:44.700 --> 01:46.800
SO HE MADE IT THROUGH
SURGERY QUICK AND EASY.

01:46.800 --> 01:48.600
NOW ALL WE HAVE TO DO
IS WATCH AND WAIT.

01:48.600 --> 01:50.300
YEAH.
IT'S ALL RIGHT.

01:50.300 --> 01:52.000
HEY, THANKS
A LOT, DOC.

01:52.000 --> 01:53.900
YOU GOT IT. JUST PAGE ME IF YOU NEED ME,

01:53.900 --> 01:55.800
'CAUSE YOU KNOW I NEVER
REALLY LEAVE THIS PLACE.

01:58.100 --> 01:59.700
HEY.
WHY WOULD HE DO THIS?

01:59.700 --> 02:01.900
I MEAN, HE MUST
HAVE BEEN POSSESSED.

02:01.900 --> 02:04.100
LOOK, BEFORE
WE BROUGHT HIM IN, HE SAID SOMETHING TO ME.

02:04.100 --> 02:06.500
HE TOLD ME HE DID THIS
TO PROTECT YOU.

02:06.500 --> 02:08.600
PROTECT ME? FROM WHAT?

02:08.600 --> 02:09.600
OR WHO.

02:10.300 --> 02:12.500
PAUL EASTMAN? NO, HE'S
HAUNTING MY FATHER.

02:12.500 --> 02:13.900
WHY WOULD HE BE
A THREAT TO ME?

02:14.400 --> 02:16.600
MAYBE THAT'S A QUESTION
FOR DEAR OLD DAD.

02:35.900 --> 02:36.900
HEY.

02:38.700 --> 02:40.700
I DON'T REALLY KNOW
IF YOU CAN HEAR ME,

02:41.600 --> 02:43.200
BUT THEY TOLD ME
MAYBE YOU COULD.

02:48.600 --> 02:51.200
LOOK, DAD,
I'M-I'M REALLY CONFUSED.

02:52.600 --> 02:53.600
I DON'T KNOW...

02:57.000 --> 02:59.200
I DON'T KNOW WHAT YOU'RE
SUPPOSED TO MEAN TO ME.

03:00.600 --> 03:03.300
I MEAN, YOU LEAVE US
WHEN I'M 9,

03:04.000 --> 03:06.700
AND THEN YOU JUST...
COME BACK.

03:07.500 --> 03:09.300
NO EXPLANATION, NOTHING.

03:12.400 --> 03:14.500
I DON'T REALLY KNOW
WHAT YOU THINK ABOUT ME.

03:18.300 --> 03:20.200
OR WHAT I REALLY
THINK ABOUT YOU.

03:22.700 --> 03:25.800
SO IT'S A REALLY BAD TIME
TO DIE, OK?

03:28.900 --> 03:32.000
BECAUSE THERE'S SO MUCH THAT WE
NEED TO KNOW ABOUT EACH OTHER.

03:35.000 --> 03:36.300
ABOUT EVERYTHING.

04:03.600 --> 04:04.800
SORRY.

04:04.800 --> 04:07.000
THERE WAS A LINE
OUT THE DOOR.

04:09.000 --> 04:11.100
I HAVE BEEN DOING THINGS
LIKE THIS ALL DAY!

04:11.100 --> 04:12.300
HEY, HEY,
DON'T WORRY ABOUT IT.

04:12.300 --> 04:13.900
BUT JUST DON'T TRY
TO PICK IT UP.

04:13.900 --> 04:15.100
I'M GONNA GET A BROOM.

04:20.600 --> 04:21.800
ARE YOU OK?

04:22.200 --> 04:23.800
YEAH, YEAH, WHATEVER.

04:25.000 --> 04:26.700
HEY, HOW IS
YOUR DAD?

04:26.700 --> 04:29.100
UH, RESTING COMFORTABLY
OR SO THEY SAY,

04:29.100 --> 04:31.100
AND IF THAT'S TRUE,
HE'S THE ONLY ONE.

04:32.100 --> 04:33.500
WHAT THE HELL
IS GOING ON?

04:33.500 --> 04:35.500
IT'S A LONG STORY, BUT I
THINK MY DAD'S BEING HAUNTED

04:35.500 --> 04:38.300
BY THIS MAN HE SENT TO
PRISON, AN INNOCENT MAN.

04:38.600 --> 04:39.600
HAUNTED HOW?

04:39.600 --> 04:43.900
MMM, I THINK THIS GHOST
JUST FIGURED OUT A WAY TO POSSESS PEOPLE
FOR A FEW MINUTES,

04:43.900 --> 04:47.100
OR AT LEAST LONG ENOUGH TO GET
THEM TO DO THE THINGS HE WANTS DONE.

04:48.100 --> 04:49.700
LIKE YOUR DAD
KILLING HIMSELF?

04:49.700 --> 04:52.200
YEAH, THAT'S ONE THEORY. THIS
DOES NOT TASTE LIKE GREEN TEA.

04:52.200 --> 04:53.400
YEAH, BECAUSE
YOU TOOK MINE.

04:53.400 --> 04:54.900
OH. SORRY.

04:54.900 --> 04:56.900
WHAT I DON'T UNDERSTAND
IS WHY NOW?

04:56.900 --> 05:00.800
I MEAN, WHY WOULD
PAUL EASTMAN WAIT 30 YEARS
TO GET VENGEANCE?

05:01.800 --> 05:04.700
ARE YOU ASKING ME LIKE YOU
ACTUALLY EXPECT AN ANSWER?

05:04.700 --> 05:07.200
YEAH, WELL,
YOU KNOW WHAT, YOU WORK ON THAT
FOR A WHILE,

05:07.200 --> 05:08.900
AND I'M GONNA GO GET US
SOME NEW GLASSES.

05:09.500 --> 05:11.700
YOU KNOW WHAT,
YOU NEED A BREAK.

05:11.700 --> 05:13.500
WE REALLY SHOULD
GO NEXT WEEK

05:13.500 --> 05:16.000
AND SEE THE TALL SHIPS COME
INTO THE HARBOR AT PIERMONT, OK?

05:16.000 --> 05:17.300
YOU MEAN DO SOMETHING FUN?

05:18.700 --> 05:20.100
I HAVE NO TRAINING FOR THAT.

05:20.800 --> 05:22.900
IT'S SETTLED!
WE ARE GOING.

